  <description><![CDATA[ 
    mapacman is a <b>multiplayer</b> online clone of pacman.
    The goal of mapacman is to score as high as possible by eating the pills around the map.
    You should avoid ghost because they will divide by two your score. But if you eat a super
    pill you can chase them! Enjoy!]]>
  </description>
